Steps to download and install Maven on Windows:
Download and install JDK.
Set environment variable JAVA_HOME
Go to the site http://maven.apache.org  and download Maven zip and select below binary zip
apache-maven-3.3.9-bin.zip

Just unzip the file to the folder you want to install maven in, like
C:/Program Files/maven

Add M2_HOME Environment variable like C:\Program Files\apache-maven-3.5.4-bin\apache-maven-3.5.4
Update the path variable, and append Maven bin folder to it i.e. %M2_HOME%\bin
To verify, run maven â€“version in the command prompt.
